data.description: Your paradise awaits with this NW Cape Coral pool home sitting on a large corner lot. New roof and update kitchen countertop where you and your family can enjoy. As you head inside this meticulous well  kept home you will notice it boasts over 1, 700 sq ft. and features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The open floor plan allows for easy entertaining whether inside or outside by your beautiful heated pool. The screened in lanai adds another 1, 000+ sq ft of living space. Need a little extra storage? The outdoor shed will be left with the property and is in the county appraisal details as permitted. With tile throughout the home, you will not have to worry about the carpets getting ruined after a long day at the beach. Speaking of beaches.... Nearby is Sanibel Island, Captiva Island, Fort Myers Beach, & Bonita Beach just to name a few of the beautiful beaches that Florida's Gulf Coast has to offer. Also, you can expect a short drive to RSW International Airport, PGD National Airport, Florida Gulf Coast University, Bell Tower Shops, Coconut Point Mall, Miromar Outlets, Sanibel Outlets, and so much more options. Check out this home before it is too late....Buyer's agents welcome!
